# Chronosync Project



Chronosync is a comprehensive productivity application with the following key features and
the tech stack

## Technical Stack
- **Frontend**: Vue.js
  - Progressive JavaScript framework
  - Component-based architecture
  - Reactive data binding
  - TypeScript may be used for type safety
  - **Nuxt UI for Vue**:
    - Collection of reusable and accessible UI components
    - Customizable design system
    - Consistent styling and theming
    - Modern and clean aesthetic

- **Backend**: Express.js
  - Node.js web application framework
  - RESTful API design
  - Authentication and authorization
  - WebSocket support for real-time updates

- **Database**: PostgreSQL
  - Relational database management system
  - Robust data persistence
  - Complex queries and relationships
  - JSON support for flexible data structures

- Cross-platform data synchronization
- Offline-first approach for mobile functionality
- Responsive design for different device sizes
- Security for user data and authentication
- Performance optimization for time tracking features
